data.description: Move in READY and LIKE-NEW Construction only 2 years old and nestled on almost 2 acres!  Step inside to discover a well-designed 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom split bedroom home adorned with vinyl plank flooring throughout the entirety of the home. No carpet! The granite countertops and STAINLESS-STEEL appliances accent the kitchen for a culinary delight. The cathedral ceiling enhances the sense of space, creating an airy ambiance that's sure to impress. Crawl space features an encapsulated crawl space, a testament to the home's energy efficiency. Outside, this property features a wide driveway that is ready for RV hookup with RV pad or add your own custom garage for easy convenience! Come experience this exceptional well-maintained home that offers a lifestyle of both comfort and like-new construction.  Just 12 miles to Interstate 40 which takes you to Knoxville or Nashville, your choice! Buyer to verify all information and measurements prior to making an informed offer.
